Title: Stoke Me a Clipper
Writer: Rob Grant (creator), Doug Naylor (creator), Paul Alexander, Doug Naylor
Actors: Chris Barrie, Craig Charles, Danny John-Jules, Robert Llewellyn
Plot: Daredevil pilot Ace Rimmer, seriously wounded, after rescuing Princess Bonjella from the Nazis, arrives on-board Starbug, to recruit Rimmer to take his place as the next Ace Rimmer. Will Rimmer continue the legacy of Ace Rimmer?
